Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線に戻れば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ クラッキング 始めるお\N待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,牧瀬 紅莉栖が… 死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I return to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:04.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラッキングは…\Nおっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中止だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Makise Kurisu dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The cracking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:52.89,Title1,,0,0,0,,Paradox Meltdown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:02:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部は？\N不明 僕 忙しかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では まゆ氏 ご武運を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Mayushii!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダル君も\Nうむ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Daru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コミマ 今日が最終日だっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is today the last day of Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 紅莉栖ちゃんも来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:13.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かわいいコスプレの子とか\Nいっぱい いるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of cute cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,べっ… 別に 興味とかないし…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not really interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン どうしたのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Okarin's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:24.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあね クラッキングを\N中止するって言ったっきり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He said we weren't doing the cracking, \Nand that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうつもりなんだか…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:34.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最高気温 35度だって！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's gonna reach a high of 35!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱中症防止には 水分を\Nこまめにとるのが大切なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydration is the best way to prevent heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日もコミマじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to Comima today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん これから行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか 気を付けてな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…\N外 日ざし 強いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really sunny out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:57.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあね トゥットゥルー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり！\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,８月17日 Ｄメールを消す度に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each D-mail I undid delayed \NMayuri's death by one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:13.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりの死は\N１日ずつ ずれていった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めは 13日に訪れていたものが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Erasing Suzuha's mail made the events \Nof the 13th occur on the 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鈴羽のメールを消すことによって\N14日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フェイリス ルカ子 萌郁…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feyris, Rukako, Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:25.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その度に 一日ずつ延びたとすると
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If each one pushed it back a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:28.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界線で\Nまゆりの死が訪れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then in this world line, Mayuri dies on the 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,17日 今日の夜８時前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, before 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまでに…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリ～ン！\Nあっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はふ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,探していたのは 見つかったのか？\Nうん！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少しで\N売り切れちゃうところだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost sold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダル君の分も確保したし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got one for Daru-kun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:49.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… オカリンの好きそうな\Nロボットアニメの本もあったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and there was a book on a \Nrobot anime I thought you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってみる？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや… 俺はいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？ せっかく来たのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し 考えたいことがあってな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:03.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこか 見に行きたい所があったら\N言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if there's anywhere you'd like to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:08.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？ もう帰る？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:13.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… あ… 何を言っている\N考え事というのは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to think about, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この会場に潜んでいる\N機関の刺客のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the Organization assassins hiding in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:19.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらを 何とかして\N出し抜かねばならんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do something to escape their clutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:22.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手に動くと\N感づかれる可能性がある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not careful, they might find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夕方まで\N予定どおりに行動するのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the original plan until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな悪い人は\Nいないと思うけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think any bad people like that are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:32.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偵察に行ってくる\N１５２０に ここで落ち合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet back here at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな？\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリ～ン\Nジュース 向こうで売ってるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're selling juice over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと５時間…\N諦めるな それまでに見つけるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before that time, find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:49.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界線を変えずに\Nまゆりが生き残る方法を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way for her to survive without \Nchanging world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.02,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？ どうして 私が\N橋田に協力しなきゃいけないの…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to help Hashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:03.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ ノート？ サークル一覧？\Nないわよ そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A notepad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A list of circles at Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラック？ ２段目…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The rack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ？ ２段目はダメ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at the second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふうっ！ リアルに訴えるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously having you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？\N俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラッキングは どうなっている？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:25.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが中止って言うから\N丸３日 ほったらかしのままよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So we haven't touched it for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかげん 説明しろ\Nいったい 何があった？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain what's going on, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが 今日 死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri will die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたわ 前に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから\Nクラッキングが必要なんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you're doing the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部が最初に送った\NＤメールを消せば…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To erase the first D-mail you sent—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:41.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！ クラッキングは なしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラッキングをしないで\Nまゆりを助ける方法を考える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think of a way to \Nsave Mayuri without the cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？\Nうっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうしなければならない\N事情が生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have changed. This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう事情よ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は 説明できない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't explain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:59.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かあるはずだ 別の方法が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別の方法って…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明して
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:08.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃないと 方法も考えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I won't be able \Nto think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力も… できない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間がないんでしょ？\N隠してる場合じゃない！ 岡部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have time for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hide things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:30.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふは～！ やっと帰ってこれた～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ オカリンは ラボ 寄ってく？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, want to stop by the lab, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは\Nご飯 食べていこうかな～って…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii was thinking of getting some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:41.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン？ 疲れちゃった？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ… ああ いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:50.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ まゆりは また…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Almost time for her to die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げるか？ いや 逃げても 結局…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. That never works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン？\N行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:11.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ オカリン 今日は なんで\Nついてきてくれたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 どこも\Nあんまり見ないままだったし…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You barely went to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見たいものとかあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to check something out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうちょっと\N案内してあげられたのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've shown you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃね\Nオカリンより詳しいことって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many things Mayushii \Nknows more than Okarin about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほとんどないから…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:36.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はね ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:39.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンと コミマ行くの\N初めてだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never gone to Comima together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしいは うれしかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so Mayushii was happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルカ子が コスプレして\N恥ずかしがっているところを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see Rukako looking \Nembarrassed in his cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見てやろうかと思ったのだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来ていなくて残念だった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだね\N来てたら 絶対 人気 出るのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if he had, he would've been really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろうな\Nそして るか君は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Ruka-kun would have gotten \Nhis photo on all the blogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんなブログに\N画像をアップされまくって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and he'd have become a worldwide superstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:04.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワールドワイドな\Nスーパースターになるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを見て まゆしぃは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Mayushii would have seen it \Nand said, "He's come a long way."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠いところに行っちゃったな～と\N思いをはせるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:12.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ…\N本当に なりそうだから困る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I could really see that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は オカリンも\Nコスプレしてくれると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be even better if Okarin cosplayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと うれしいかも\N考えておこう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホント？\Nその代わり まゆりも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange, you'd also have to cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コスプレして参加するのだぞ\Nええっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな… だとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... We'll call Rukako and Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルカ子に クリスティーナも呼ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:30.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして ２人がコスプレするように\Nまゆりが説得するのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can convince them to cosplay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それができたら 真打ちとして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, then I,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この 狂気のﾏｯﾄﾞｻｲｴﾝﾃｨｽﾄ\N鳳凰院 凶真が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma, mad scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コミマに降臨しようではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,shall make my cosplay debut at Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか… 道は険しいね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to be hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 紅莉栖ちゃんは\N脈ありだったし…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kurisu-chan was interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so Mayushii will try her best to \Ndo it by the next Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:47.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃ 次のコミマまでに\N頑張ってみるね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次… あっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…\Nあれ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My watch isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:58.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃのカイちゅ～\N止まっちゃってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしいな さっき…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ！ ああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wound—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やだ！ もう やだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't go through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来たのに\Nどうして まだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン！\Nここで じっとしていろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:17.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変えてやる！ 運命を…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:20.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,因果を 自分の手で！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll stop it from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:24.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が…\N俺が ここで はねられれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I let that car hit me... If I die here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命を投げ出せば\N何かが変わるはずだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}something has to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… まゆり？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:50.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカ… リン？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:55.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘ… やっと…\Nやっと 役に立った…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... Finally, I was useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii was useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:05.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンの役に立てたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:11.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカ… リン… の…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ まゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:26.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここからじゃ\Nあまり 星 見えないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see the stars from here, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなの あんまりだろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.60,Sign21A,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you. \NKurisu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ クラッキング 始めるお
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部？ あ…\Nあっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまで そこにいるつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人にさせてくれと\N言ったはずだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:34.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いた けど 屋上に上がったまま\N何時間も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've been up here, on the roof, for hours
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,物音一つ立てずにいたら 心配す…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,without a sound. I got worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:39.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ いや… しないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not worried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:44.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えて どうして\Nクラッキングをやめるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前だって よくないと言ったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You yourself said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:52.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タイーホフラグが立って\Nビビったんですね 分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought the FBI would come, \Nand you got scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to be thought of as a law-abiding citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,順法精神に目覚めたと言ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,らしくないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもの独善的な態度は\Nどこへ行ったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your normal, hotshot attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気のマッドサイエンティスト…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The great mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I act like that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,独善的でなんかいられるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気のマッドサイエンティスト？\N鳳凰院 凶真？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの 全部 妄想だ！ 設定だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気付かなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:19.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初対面で気付いてましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew within five seconds of meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:23.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか\Nまた タイムリープしてきたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you time leap again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何があった？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:30.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さんざん\N相談に乗ってやったでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've helped you with everything so far, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:32.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今更 遠慮するな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までも ２人で考えて\Nここまで来たんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made it this far by \Nthinking things through together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ここまで来た｣ か…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:44.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鈴羽や フェイリス ルカ子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha and Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To come this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:48.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの思いを犠牲にして\Nやっと たどり着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I sacrificed the things they loved the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:52.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが こんな結末なのかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, this is how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして… ううっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:08.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 岡部\Nあんた あの時 泣いてたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe, you were crying back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋田も心配してた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida was concerned, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖い夢でも見たんじゃないかって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought maybe you had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部の力になりたいの！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:36.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７月28日 俺は まゆりと\N中鉢博士の会見に出かけた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,July 28th...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri and I went to \NDr. Nakabachi's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I saw Makise Kurise collapsed\Nafter being stabbed by someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:44.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者かに刺され 倒れている\N牧瀬 紅莉栖を発見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:48.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電話レンジにつながっていた\Nダルの携帯にメールを送った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent a text to Daru's cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which was connected to the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１通目のＤメール
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The first D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The message that moved us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線から α世界線に\N移動することになった元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,from the beta world line to the alpha world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＳＥＲＮに捉えられた\Nそのメールを消し
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Deleting that message from SERN's database,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線に戻るということ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and returning to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり その世界に戻るということ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,means going back to that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:11.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線に戻れば…\NあのＤメールを消せば…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we return to the beta world line...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we undo that first D-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てあげなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりか？\Nあっ… うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:43.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？\Nあのね ダル君から聞いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daru-kun told me you were acting odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン なんか変だったって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:49.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に何もない ダルの勘違いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:55.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんね\Nまゆしぃ コミマに夢中で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii's been so busy with Comima,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:59.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンのこと\N見てあげられなかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,she couldn't spend time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:03.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのね 昔 よく まゆしぃに\Nいろんな お話してくれたよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you used to talk to Mayushii about \Nall kinds of stuff, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:07.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと… 機関には幹部が４人いて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There were four Organization generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲップと スダチと\N声優と ジャコ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Geppu, Sudachi, Seiyuu, and Jakkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbu, Suzaku, Seiryuu, Byakko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄武と朱雀と青龍と白虎だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… そう それ\Nそういうね オカリンの話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked hearing about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっても面白かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ…\Nあのね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:27.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃのこと\N重荷に感じたら 言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mayushii is ever a burden, tell me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ とりあえず 切るね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you alone for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mayushii can do anything for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:31.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし まゆしぃに\Nお話できることがあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,call me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつでも 電話してね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり おい…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに行くべきよ\N岡部の声 聞いてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,From your voice, I can guess what she was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:42.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが 何 言ってたか\N大体 分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go see her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに会いに行くべきよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to come up with any answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のことは 今 ここで話してても\N何も答えは出ない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you do stay here, talking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you were sitting here alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:53.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから あんたは 今まで\N一人で悩んでた そうでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should go see Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら\Nまゆりに会いに行くべきよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで\Nただ あんたに心配されても
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that will happen if you \Nstay and worry is that you'll hurt my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:01.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のプライドが傷つくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:04.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先 行くわね\Nあっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:16.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃです\N今 電話に出られません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mayushii. I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺だ\Nやっぱり まゆ氏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the cosplayers said Mayushii left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:25.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かなり前に帰ったって\Nコスプレの子が言ってたお
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to see me because it's Obon. \NRight, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:55.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お盆だから おばあちゃん\N会いに来てくれたんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:17:00.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのね\N最近 怖い夢ばっかり見るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been having scary dreams lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢の中でね いつも\Nまゆしぃは ひどい目に遭うの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the dreams, terrible things happen to Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets shot with a pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:10.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピストルで パンて撃たれたり\N車の事故に巻き込まれたり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or she's in a car accident or run over by a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電車に ひかれたり…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything seems like it really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで 本当のことみたいで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary, and it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっごく怖くて 痛くて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to scream for help, as loud as I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:23.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か助けてって\N一生懸命 声 出すんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出せなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have these dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:30.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして そんな夢 見るのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end of the dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でね その夢の最後には
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:37.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも\Nオカリンが助けに来てくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin always comes to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:41.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは ｢オカリン\Nありがとう｣って言うんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii says, "Thank you, Okarin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't hear her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:44.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その声も\Nオカリンには聞こえなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:51.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃのこと抱きしめて\Nとっても悲しそうな顔をして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He holds Mayushii, and he looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:57.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 泣かないんだけど\N一生懸命 我慢してるのが分かるの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And he never cries, \Nbut you can tell he really wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mayushii says, "I'm sorry." \NBut he doesn't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:01.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから まゆしぃも\N｢ごめんね｣って言うんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,声は やっぱり 届かなくて\N目が覚めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ… ごめんね 楽しい話するね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk about something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近\Nラボメンが すごく増えたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, there are lots of new lab members!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖ちゃんでしょ 萌郁さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And Moeka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,るか君に フェリスちゃん\Nそれと 鈴さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ruka-kun, and Feyris-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, it was just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:23.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初は ２人だけだったのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:27.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖ちゃんなんか\Nすっごい 頭 良くて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu-chan is super-smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And she talks about all these \Nreally hard things with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:32.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンと 難しい話なんか\Nいっぱいしてね にぎやかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin looks happy that he gets to talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンも\Nたくさん話せて楽しそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:41.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもね たまには思い出すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, sometimes I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:47.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に まゆしぃが\Nラボに押しかけた頃のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time Mayushii went to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the beginning of spring, but it was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:51.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,春先なのに\N珍しく 雪が降ってて…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to the lab after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:56.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校が終わって ラボに行くとね\Nオカリンはいないの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:19:00.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でね お部屋の\N片づけしたりしてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was cleaning up the room, he came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンが来てね\N｢おかえり｣って言うと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, "Welcome back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And he didn't say, "I'm back."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ただいま｣とは言わなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Good work."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:10.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ご苦労｣って答えて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, every day after that, I'd go there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのあとは 毎日 ２時間ぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for about two hours, and we'd barely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほとんど お話もしないで\N過ごしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:22.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌な沈黙とかじゃなくって\Nただ そこにいるって感じで…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't bad. We were simply there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passed so slowly, and it was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:27.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆっくり ゆっくり\N優しい時間が流れてて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii thought she really was like a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:32.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは\N本当に人質みたいだなって…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:34.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か いいことでもあったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:39.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん！ いいことはなかったけど\Nあったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing good happened, but it was good anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand... You saw some kind of illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか 幻想を見たのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may be an attack by \NOrganization General Illusion Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:47.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,機関の幹部 幻想案内からの\N攻撃の可能性がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか… じゃあ 気を付けなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I bet that Illusion Contactor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも\Nその イリュージョン子だくさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢コンダクター｣だ\Nああ… うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think he's a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:59.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人は\N多分 悪い人じゃないと思うな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I haven't spent much time \Ntalking with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:07.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近ね オカリンと お話する時間\Nちょっと減っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be that when I saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:12.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前は オカリンの顔を見れば\N何 考えてるか 分かったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近は 分からなくなっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:22.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ なんか とっても つらそうで\N苦しそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like he's really suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like he's always about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:25.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもいつも 泣きだしそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know he's thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:30.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは まゆしぃのことなんだって\N分かって…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンの重荷には\Nなりたくないのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a burden to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I was talking about \Nsomething sad again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:38.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんね なんか また\N悲しい話になっちゃったね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Mayushii's been lonely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:43.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃ ちょっと さみしく\Nなっちゃったのかもしれないね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おばあちゃん いつまでも\Nこのままじゃいられないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, I can't stay this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:59.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オ… オカリンだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして ここが分かったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I always know where my hostage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:09.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人質が どこにいるのか\N俺は 常に把握しているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:14.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから お前は\N俺の手から逃れられん 絶対にだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't ever escape from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:17.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんまり 無理しちゃダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:25.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に心配されるほど\Nこの 鳳凰院 凶真は 柔ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Hououin Kyouma,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,am not so weak that I need you \Nto worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes that I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:31.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話せる時が来たら 全てを話す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:35.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん\N帰るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ でも その前に…\N分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get another Upa gatchapon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーぱのガチャガチャ\Nやっていくんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘヘ…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.22,0:29:53.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線に戻れば
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.18,0:29:56.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのＤメールを消せば
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.18,0:29:58.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が死ぬ
